               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430227-name-1137" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430227-name-1137" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430227-name-1137" type="surname" value="LYNCH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430227-name-1137" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN LYNCH</persName>
                  </hi>. I am carman to William Bennett Bailey—the prisoners have been employed by him. Between seven and eight o'clock on the 24th of Feb., I hung up my harness—about ten o'clock I was sent for, and the door of the place where the harness was was open—(it was locked when I left it)—the harness was all gone—this is it—it is my master's—they must have used a false key to get in.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
