                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable H</hi> 74.) On the evening of the 24th of Feb. I saw Burns with this harness in a sack, about a quarter before nine—Wheatley was in his company—I had seen Wheatley give Burns a lift up with it on his shoulder—when I detected Burns, Wheatley passed by.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Burns.</hi> I am a porter; I was employed to carry this.</p>
